  "instructions": [
    "Fry the sesame seeds in a hot skillet over medium heat, stirring frequently, until golden brown.",
    "Add the coconut oil to the skillet and swirl to combine.",
    "Add the crushed cardamom and stir for 10 seconds.",
    "Add the dates and stir to combine.",
    "Add the nimono broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the rum (if using) and ghee (if using).",
    "Transfer the hash to a hot stone plate and serve immediately.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with additional sesame seeds and cardamom, if desired.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!",
